      "skos:definition": {
        "@value": "quotient of the thermal diffusion ratio stem:[k_T] (<<t9-40.1>>), and the product of the local amount-of-substance fractions stem:[x_\"A\"], stem:[x_\"B\"] (<<t9-13>>) of two substances stem:[\"A\"] and stem:[\"B\"]:\n\n[stem%unnumbered]\n++++\nalpha_T = k_T//(x_\"A\" x_\"B\")\n++++\n",
